##TEXT STYLES

- *SIX SEVEN* "*" Single star on each side of the word = *Italic*
- **SIX SEVENNNN** "**" Two stars on each side of the word = **BOLD**
- ***SIX SEVEEENNNNnn*** "***" Three stars on each side of the word = ***BOLD Italic***
